author: Written by: Kelly Weston, Digital Content Producer
title: Man arrives at hospital with gunshot wound to stomach
text:
NEW ORLEANS, LA (WVUE) - New Orleans police are investigating a shooting after the victim showed up at hospital with a stomach wound.
The incident occurred just after 4 p.m. near the intersection of Harmony and Dryades streets.
Police said the investigation is still in the preliminary stages and there was no other information to release.
The victim's condition is not known.
